---
import Layout from '../layouts/PageWithTitle.astro';
import { GITHUB_REPO } from '../consts';
---

<Layout
	title="The Company"
	description="Embedded firmware benchmarks and agent evaluation for Fieldwork."
>
	<p>
		Fieldwork evaluates coding agents on real embedded hardware: STM32 Nucleo boards, XMOS xcore devices,
		and the tasks defined in the <a href={GITHUB_REPO}>fieldwork-firmware</a> repository.
	</p>
	<p>
		Each benchmark bundles a rendered task, runs an agent in a sandboxed toolchain environment, and scores
		the result with platform-specific observers (UART traces, VCD waveforms, monitor plugins, and more).
	</p>
	<p>
		Use this blog for release notes, benchmark methodology, and write-ups on individual tasks and rollouts.
	</p>
	<h1>The People</h1>
	<div class="people-grid">
		<article class="person-card">
			<figure>
				<div class="headshot-placeholder" role="img" aria-label="Headshot placeholder for Person 1"></div>
				<figcaption>Person 1, Role</figcaption>
			</figure>
			<p>Short bio for Person 1. Add a brief blurb describing their background and focus area.</p>
		</article>
		<article class="person-card">
			<figure>
				<div class="headshot-placeholder" role="img" aria-label="Headshot placeholder for Person 2"></div>
				<figcaption>Person 2, Role</figcaption>
			</figure>
			<p>Short bio for Person 2. Add a brief blurb describing their background and focus area.</p>
		</article>
		<article class="person-card">
			<figure>
				<div class="headshot-placeholder" role="img" aria-label="Headshot placeholder for Person 3"></div>
				<figcaption>Person 3, Role</figcaption>
			</figure>
			<p>Short bio for Person 3. Add a brief blurb describing their background and focus area.</p>
		</article>
		<article class="person-card">
			<figure>
				<div class="headshot-placeholder" role="img" aria-label="Headshot placeholder for Person 4"></div>
				<figcaption>Person 4, Role</figcaption>
			</figure>
			<p>Short bio for Person 4. Add a brief blurb describing their background and focus area.</p>
		</article>
	</div>
</Layout>

<style>
	.people-grid {
		display: grid;
		grid-template-columns: repeat(2, minmax(0, 1fr));
		gap: 1.5rem;
		margin-top: 1rem;
	}

	.person-card {
		padding: 1rem;
		border: 1px solid #d9d9d9;
		border-radius: 0.75rem;
	}

	.person-card figure {
		margin: 0 0 0.75rem;
	}

	.headshot-placeholder {
		aspect-ratio: 1 / 1;
		width: 100%;
		border-radius: 0.75rem;
		background: linear-gradient(135deg, #efefef, #d9d9d9);
		margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
	}

	.person-card figcaption {
		font-weight: 600;
	}

	.person-card p {
		margin: 0;
	}

	@media (max-width: 768px) {
		.people-grid {
			grid-template-columns: 1fr;
		}
	}
</style>
